name: Starmane Nebula Whisper
text: In the ever-deepening dusk, Starmane Nebula Whisper emerged, evolution of Twilight Gleamfang. With a cosmic trail etching skyward arcs, it danced amongst celestial realms. An aura of elder magic clung to its shimmering form, evoking tales of its mythic precursor, now whispered by the stars themselves.
